data.description: Darling and immaculately kept one level ranch. This is not your cookie cutter Costco remodel folks. You have to come see this vibrant home with personality! The important basics....New roof and sewer line in 2016, updated kitchen and baths and new flooring. Yard features room to park RV or toys, firepit area, garden and a peaceful place to chill. Convenient location close to Jones Farms Intel & shopping yet 5 minutes to the freeway. Don't let this one get away! [Home Energy Score = 5. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10196017]
